### Start payment (manual) - amount is fetched from Transactions API, customerId validated for fraud protection
POST http://localhost:5264/api/payments/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
}

### Confirm payment
POST http://localhost:5264/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/confirm

### Fail payment
POST http://localhost:5264/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/fail
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient funds"
}

### Get payment
GET http://localhost:5264/api/payments/{{paymentId}}
